Test Dataset Birth Weight

df_opt_birthwt.Rd

Dataset from Baystate Medical Center in Springfield, Massachusetts (Hosmer et. al. 1998)

data(df_opt_birthwt)

Format

csv

Source

https://onlinelibrary.wiley.com/doi/book/10.1002/9781118548387

References

HOSMER, D.W., HOSMER, T., LE CESSIE, S. and LEMESHOW, S. (1997), A COMPARISON OF GOODNESS‐OF‐FIT TESTS FOR THE LOGISTIC REGRESSION MODEL. Statist. Med., 16: 965-980. doi:10.1002/(SICI)1097-0258(19970515)16:9<965::AID-SIM509>3.0.CO;2-O
